<DOC><DOCNO> DOE2-32-0817 </DOCNO><TEXT>The PWH group worldwide offers a new model of unloader which completesthe series of continuous ship unloaders. In the article this PWH unloader'Screw Conveyor System' is described in its most important elements andfunctions. The unloader is - above all - designed for the unloading ofinland vessels, barges and motor coasters. Apart from fertilizers ofall kinds many other fine grained materials such as derivatives, cement,fine coal, corn, and elements for the chemical industry can be unloaded.The unloader is designed for 100 t/h to approximately 800 t/h.</TEXT></DOC>